Assembly","content":["300 g dried spaghetti","extra virgin olive oil, for drizzling"]}],"id":"r247616","imageLink":"https:\/\/4.bp.blogspot.com\/-8_1xF4ep10E\/XZVQfaYbTuI\/AAAAAAAAdBw\/ZWde6FR9hJccZcVirmxRVPWdH4-kgYfewCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_ORGm-wwtAsXTMHS-.png","title":"Cheeseboard Spaghetti","publishedAt":"2018-02-05T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"30.9 g","fat":"43 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"75 g","calories":"3604 kJ \/ 861 kcal"},"usefulItems":"non-stick frying pan, colander, large bowl, large saucepan, serving plates, hob","hintsAndTricks":["Use cheese you may have leftover from a cheeseboard or dinner party. A combination of a creamy cheese such as brie, some sharp cheddar, and a strong blue works well.","Give leftover cheese a new lease of life with this simple yet flavourful pasta dish."],"basicInfo":["easy","20m","45m","4 portions"]}